                        <persName role="art" cert="medium" key="person_f6875">Shīvā Lāl (1817–1887)</persName>,
                        known as <addName type="epithet">Shāhī Muṣavvir</addName> (Royal Painter). <list>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="2a">2a,</locus>
                              <dimensions type="illustration" unit="mm">
                                 <height>72</height>
                                 <width>82</width>
                              </dimensions><p> The cat makes its way to the tavern.</p></item>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="2b">2b,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>86</height>
                                 <width>81</width>
                              </dimensions><p> The mice cavort in the tavern.</p></item>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="3b">3b,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>111</height>
                                 <width>83</width>
                              </dimensions><p> The cat seizes a mouse.</p></item>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="4b">4b,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>150</height>
                                 <width>93</width>
                              </dimensions><p> The cat repents in the mosque for killing the
                                 mouse.</p></item>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="5a">5a,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>25</height>
                                 <width>38</width>
                              </dimensions><p> A mouse reports the cat's repentance.</p></item>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="5b">5b,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>96</height>
                                 <width>81</width>
                              </dimensions><p> A delegation of seven mice brings gifts to the
                                 repentant cat.</p></item>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="6a">6a,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>108</height>
                                 <width>103</width>
                              </dimensions><p> The cat kills five of the mice delegation but two
                                 escape.</p></item>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="7b">7b,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>148</height>
                                 <width>108</width>
                              </dimensions><p> The king of the mice assembles his army.</p></item>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="8b">8b,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>108</height>
                                 <width>122</width>
                              </dimensions><p> The cat appears before the king of the cats to
                                 account for his actions.</p></item>
