                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>112</height>
                                 <width>97</width>
                              </dimensions><p> The captive cat appears before the king of the
                                 mice.</p></item>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="9b">9b,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>68 </height>
                                 <width>103</width>
                              </dimensions><p> The vizier of the mice accompanies the cat on
