                           <item>Folio <locus from="10a">10a,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>103 </height>
                                 <width>85</width>
                              </dimensions><p> Cats slaughter the vizier of the mice.</p></item>
                           <item>Folio <locus from="11a">11a,</locus><dimensions type="illustration"
                                 unit="mm">
                                 <height>124</height>
                                 <width>114</width>
                              </dimensions><p> The army of the mice captures the cat.</p></item>
